# Production proxy list for the wallet generator.
# One entry per line. Format:  scheme://username:password@host:port
#
# Supported schemes: http, https, socks5, socks5h
#
# IMPORTANT: copy this file to `proxies.txt` (NO `.example`) and fill in
# real credentials. `proxies.txt` is in .gitignore and will never be
# committed.
#
# The script automatically injects a unique sticky-session id into the
# username for each wallet, in the form:
#
#     scheme://USER-session-wXXX-NNNNN:PASSWORD@host:port
#
# This convention works out of the box with:
#   - Smartproxy / Decodo  (recommended)
#   - Bright Data
#   - Oxylabs
#   - IPRoyal
#
# A single base endpoint is enough — every wallet gets its own sticky
# session. If you provide multiple endpoints (e.g. different geos), the
# script round-robins across them.
#
# ---- examples (NOT real, replace with yours) -----------------------------
# Smartproxy / Decodo residential:
# http://YOUR_USER:YOUR_PASS@gate.decodo.com:7000
#
# Bright Data residential (zone format):
# http://brd-customer-hl_XXXX-zone-residential:YOUR_PASS@brd.superproxy.io:22225
#
# Oxylabs residential:
# http://customer-YOUR_USER:YOUR_PASS@pr.oxylabs.io:7777
#
# IPRoyal residential:
# http://YOUR_USER:YOUR_PASS@geo.iproyal.com:12321
#
# Generic SOCKS5 (e.g. self-hosted):
# socks5h://YOUR_USER:YOUR_PASS@1.2.3.4:1080
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
